OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBanks summoned on mortgages
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter rates rise shock     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Banks and building societies are to    
OL,6, meet Chancellor Jeremy Hunt to discuss 
OL,7, the upheaval in the mortgage market.   
OL,9,FIt comes after Thursday's shock        
OL,10,Fdecision by the Bank of England to hike
OL,11,Frates to 5%, up from 4.5%, as it tries 
OL,12,Fto tackle persistently high inflation. 
OL,14,FThe government and lenders are under   
OL,15,Fpressure to do more to help those      
OL,16,Fstruggling with rising mortgage rates. 
OL,18,FBut Mr Hunt and Prime Minister Rishi   
OL,19,FSunak have so far dismissed suggestions
OL,20,Fof the government stepping in.         
